OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost showers
OL,6,Feasing this evening to leave clear
OL,7,Fspells initially. Turning cloudier
OL,8,Fovernight with some showery rain in
OL,9,Fthe far south by dawn. Chilly in any
OL,10,Fclear skies in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,13,Fshowery rain. Turning brighter in the
OL,14,Ffar south and east with heavy showers
OL,15,Fbreaking out. Staying cloudy in the
OL,16,Fnorth. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
