OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarmer
OL,6,Fon Saturday with heavy showers by the
OL,7,Fafternoon, merging into longer spells
OL,8,Fof rain overnight. Drier on Sunday but
OL,9,Fbreezier and turning cooler with
OL,10,Fpatchy rain on Monday.
